title: Helen discusses blending Vietnamese and American culture

media:group.media:title: Helen discusses blending Vietnamese and American culture
media:group.media:description:
Helen, a “Being Asian in America” documentary participant, discusses how she wants to teach her children both American and Vietnamese traditions so they can know both and choose which is best for them in life.   

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
